Orolingual tremor (kinematically detected)

dat <- read.csv("dat_tremor.csv", header=T)

dat <- dat %>%
  select(-trial)

dat <- dat %>%
  mutate(isTremor = ifelse((is.na(peak) | amplitude < 0.16), 0, 1))

#for each participant, isTremor = 1 for any trial/sensor means that tremor above 3 Hz was detected at an RMS amplitude of at least 0.16 in one of the axes (in case multiple directions: strongest one was taken for peak/amplitude calculations)

Visualize the prevalence of acoustic and kinematic tremor

contingency_table <- table(dat$isTremor, dat$group, dat$task)
df <- as.data.frame(contingency_table)
names(df) <- c("isTremor", "group", "task", "count")

df <- df %>%
  group_by(task, group) %>%
  mutate(total_count = sum(count),
         Percentage = (count/total_count)*100) %>%
  ungroup()

df$Tremor <- ifelse(df$isTremor == 1, "yes", "no")

ggplot(df, aes(x = Tremor, y = Percentage, fill = Tremor)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", position = "dodge") + 
  theme_bw(base_size = 16) +
  facet_grid(task~group) +
  geom_text(aes(label = sprintf("%.1f%%", Percentage)),
            position = position_dodge(width = 0.9), 
            vjust = 2.5) +
    geom_text(aes(label = sprintf("%.1f%%", Percentage)),
            position = position_dodge(width = 0.9), 
            vjust = -1) +
  ggtitle("Prevalence of orolingual kinematic tremor")

contingency_table <- table(voice_dat2$isTremor, voice_dat2$group, voice_dat2$type)
df <- as.data.frame(contingency_table)
names(df) <- c("isTremor", "group", "type", "count")

df <- df %>%
  group_by(type, group) %>%
  mutate(total_count = sum(count),
         Percentage = (count/total_count)*100) %>%
  ungroup()

df$Tremor <- ifelse(df$isTremor == 1, "yes", "no")

ggplot(df, aes(x = Tremor, y = Percentage, fill = Tremor)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", position = "dodge") + 
  theme_bw(base_size = 16) +
  facet_grid(type~group) +
  geom_text(aes(label = sprintf("%.1f%%", Percentage)),
            position = position_dodge(width = 0.9), 
            vjust = 10) +
  geom_text(aes(label = sprintf("%.1f%%", Percentage)),
            position = position_dodge(width = 0.9), 
            vjust = -2.5) +
  ggtitle("Prevalence of voice tremor")

                  variable.name = "measure",
                  value.name = "value")

dat2_long$measure <- as.factor(dat2_long$measure)

dat2_long <- dat2_long %>%
  group_by(measure) %>%
  mutate(mean_value = mean(value, na.rm=T),
         sd_value = sd(value, na.rm=T)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  mutate(z.value = (value - mean_value) / sd_value)
